<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Haiti Update: UCF Collecting Donations On Campus</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By UCF Staff
		
		<span class="date">Updated Jan. 22, 2010</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2019/en_US/vigilsilhoriz.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: James Crawford/UCF Engineers Without Borders</p>
			
			<p>UCF students remembered earthquake victims and vowed to help survivors recover during a recent candlelight vigil.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=002400417c223ec20125ae9931fd004fdf">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
